Okay so far we have got a basic structure, we have not yet connected any API. 

WHY?
    - GPT or Claude can code the HTML and CSS. But can not graphically show or host the site
    - We need a hosting API such as netlify or Github Actions
    - In order to generate images or svg, we need something like DALL-E or MidJourney

We will be using Google Gemini free tier API for generating code.
We will use netlify API for hosting. (also free)

Workflow (AI code) (1 API call made to AI per website) = 

ask the hardcoded questions --> gather info on type of website --> compile a prompt to send to LLM via API --> recieve html and css code for the website --> deploy the website code on netlify using the netlify API. 

PROMPT
make me a website, the name of my brand is informia, the theme is dark colours, the vibe is fun and the purpose is a portfolio website for the brand. make me a frontend page theme using html css as a template to use

