1) SCRAPER
    It is not just a web scraper, it is also a web crawler WHICH scrapes data from sites. Although a model can be made, the implementation on a large scale level will need high computational power and a database which can store data from all sites scraped.
    The other issue is the legality of the situation, not all websites allow scraping and most websites also only allow crawling to some extent (enough for them to be indexed by browsers)

2) Drag n Drop feature.
    - svg for logos & icons
    - png for images

